ScalaNLP-Core consists of libraries for NLP and Machine Learning.
The library consists of two parts: 

* ScalaNLP-Data: Libraries for managing datasets and job pipelines.
* ScalaNLP-Learn: Machine Learning and Optimization.

(c) David Hall and Daniel Ramage, 2009 - 

This project can be built with sbt 0.11.2

See https://github.com/scalanlp/scalanlp-core/wiki/Tour for some examples.
